reviews.text: Great place for hotpot. Very affordable price given the variety of food items. But don't expect to get high quality food.

really packed with people, with a 2 hour time limit from when you sit down. The broth seems on the salty side but really flavourful. The spicy broth was nice and strong. Lots of choices for ingredients and also good selection of drinks and dessert. Well worth the price (:
Serve hot pot for one person, really appreciate it, most other hot pot restaurants reject. Polite staff

Nice environment AYCE hot pot with lots of variety of choice.  They had 3 type of beef 2 type of pork and 1 type of lamb for u to order.  Shrimp is fresh and finger long.  A dessert counter,  a ice cream counter in additional to popsicle counter with different of choice of sweet.  Self serve drink with juice/soft drink/beer without limit.  Within 2 hr could fill up anyone with different preference.
Love this place. Best value for your buck!

reviews.text: 想餓死就食😂

직원들이 영어를 대부분 못하지만 친절해요.
카스.하이트 캔맥주 무제한.
고기는 쬐끔이지만
가격대비 만족스런 몽콕 훠궈 입니다.
거의 한국식 무제한 같아요.
사장님이 한국계 ? 
아님
한국을 많이 펜치마케팅 했을듯 ㅋㅋ
Great place for hotpot. Very affordable price given the variety of food items. But don't expect to get high quality food.

훠궈 무한리필 식당
고기의 질이 좋다
다양한 식재료들이 어울러져 모두 무료로 제공된다.
음료수와 맥주도 무료이다
고기(소고기, 양고기, 돼지고기. 생새우등)는 주문서를 통해 5가지정도 제공받을 수 있다.
야재 및 기타 재료는 제공받은 접시에 원하는 만큼 가져올 수 있다.
디저트로 아이스크림 바. 쿠키, 케익 등도 있다.
육수는 4가지로 선택할 수 있으며 
채식주의자를 위한 육수도 별도로 있다.
銅鑼灣火鍋放題，食物質素不是很高，但勝在火煱料款式多，飲品選擇多，無加一。

reviews.text: Reasonable price and foods were great
Reasonable price with fairly good food quality,
Great food great place great value

The place is nice, has a lot of choice in food as well.
The waiters are friendly, however there're too many customers and the reception lady was too busy to deal with all of them.

Considering it's only $158 per person (total 5 of us) and getting buffet style hot pot for 2 hours I think it's worthy.

Not a good choice to come at Friday night as you will need to wait for a long time to finally get a table.
Good and not expensive. Very full better have booking.

reviews.text: 地方狹窄，2小時任食，未夠半小時前已摧結賬，敗筆之舉！
食物味道、湯底係可以既，有人生日會播生日歌，大枱好啲，二人枱比較細比較迫，種類都多選擇，要訂位
未夠鐘就收走餐具。野食幾好都係用。
地方好、食物多款、飲品多、服務員一般
雖限時進食 但食物質素種類保持水準
